<paragraph blockId="5.[189,1398,568,638]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">
This species was correctly interpreted by 
<bibRefCitation author="Moure" box="[686,851,568,595]" firstAuthor="Moure" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" pagination="257 - 261" refId="ref21446" refString="Moure, J. S. 2002. O subgenero Centris (Aphemisia) Ayala: notas complementares e descricao de uma nova especie (Hymenoptera, Apoidea). Revista brasileira de Entomologia 46 (3): 257 - 261. https: // doi. org / 10.1590 / s 0085 - 56262002000300006" type="journal article" year="2002">Moure (2002)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation author="Moure" box="[912,1150,568,595]" etAl="et al." firstAuthor="Moure" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" pagination="83 - 142" refId="ref21502" refString="Moure J. S., Melo G. A. R. &amp; Vivallo F. 2007. Centridini Cockerell &amp; Cockerell. In: Moure J. S., Urban D. &amp; Melo G. A. R. (orgs) Catalogue of Bees (Hymenoptera, Apoidea) in the Neotropical Region: 83 - 142. Sociedade Brasileira de Entomologia, Curitibrazil." type="book chapter" year="2007">
Moure 
<emphasis box="[999,1059,568,594]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">et al.</emphasis>
(2007)
</bibRefCitation>
. Erroneously, 
<bibRefCitation author="Moure" firstAuthor="Moure" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" pagination="257 - 261" refId="ref21446" refString="Moure, J. S. 2002. O subgenero Centris (Aphemisia) Ayala: notas complementares e descricao de uma nova especie (Hymenoptera, Apoidea). Revista brasileira de Entomologia 46 (3): 257 - 261. https: // doi. org / 10.1590 / s 0085 - 56262002000300006" type="journal article" year="2002">Moure (2002)</bibRefCitation>
considered the specimen housed at 
<collectionCode box="[689,779,612,638]" country="USA" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/142r-0w94" name="Smithsonian Institution, National Museum of Natural History" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" type="Museum">NMNH</collectionCode>
